Why you?

01:26:07.579 --> 01:26:09.539
What’s so much more acceptable about you?

01:26:12.125 --> 01:26:14.670
And then I realized,
you’re the fucked up one.

01:26:14.753 --> 01:26:16.630
You’re the one who threw everything away.

01:26:20.217 --> 01:26:23.470
I want to know some things.
I have some questions for you.

01:26:23.553 --> 01:26:25.639
- Preston.
- I have questions for you.

01:26:25.889 --> 01:26:28.809
- Preston did not do anything.
- Nobody said he did.

01:26:30.060 --> 01:26:32.104
Irregardless, I would like to know,

01:26:32.187 --> 01:26:33.998
what you were doing out
on those railroad tracks.

01:26:34.022 --> 01:26:36.358
And why was it you, of all people,
who found my son?

01:26:36.441 --> 01:26:37.526
He was trying to get warm.

01:26:37.609 --> 01:26:39.653
