01:27:34.583 --> 01:27:37.711
Um... I was... I was...

01:27:39.004 --> 01:27:41.214
I was going to. I...

01:27:42.340 --> 01:27:43.884
He, uh...

01:27:44.134 --> 01:27:46.136
