- What?

01:28:14.080 --> 01:28:15.165
Before he ran off.

01:28:16.666 --> 01:28:17.667
No, you didn’t.

01:28:20.003 --> 01:28:21.003
Yeah, I did.

01:28:21.421 --> 01:28:23.381
What? You...

