01:29:00.252 --> 01:29:02.838
You smug little fuck. You let it happen!

01:29:04.297 --> 01:29:06.758
No, Mitchell!

01:29:07.259 --> 01:29:08.259
Dad!

01:29:08.343 --> 01:29:10.720
- Oh, my God!
- Oh!

