01:31:09.589 --> 01:31:13.009
He's, uh... He’s a grown up now. Mostly.

01:31:13.093 --> 01:31:15.345
He’ll, uh, be going to graduate school
in the city.

01:31:15.428 --> 01:31:16.304
Nice.

